•I have been out searching for this for a while now and I must say it works like magic! This cute little skin regime helps me to keep up a supple, radiant and glowing skin while helping to minimize any signs of ageing, puffiness and skin dehydration

So what’s this regime we are talking about? What all would you have to do?
Its super easy and there are just two products from The Billbergia:

24k Carat Gold Professional Face Serum:
✅Nourishes Skin
✅Helps Minimize Wrinkle Depth
✅Helps in Hydrating and Firming
✅Fights Signs of Ageing

Under Eye Anti-Wrinkle & Anti-Ageing Cream:
✅Reduces Puffiness
✅Anti-Ageing
✅Removes Dark Circles
✅Anti Wrinkle
✅Hydrates Dry Eye Skin

How to use?
24k Carat Gold Professional Face Serum:
Wash your face & Neck and pat it well. After cleaning , pump out 2-3 drops of our face serum onto your palm and gently massage it onto your face and neck till it absorbs well into your skin. To get the best results, use the product twice a day after your morning bath and before you hit the bed. and enjoy your healthier skin.

Under Eye Anti-Wrinkle & Anti-Ageing Cream:
Dab it lightly around the eye area carefully. Gently massage our under eye cream in circular motion till its absorbed in the skin well. For best results, use twice a day.
